Ella Hunt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ella_Hunt 0 Ella Hunt (born 29 April 1998) is an English actress, known for Intruders (2011), Les Misérables (2012), Robot Overlords (2014), and Anna and the Apocalypse (2017). Since 2016, she has played the role of Ellie Marsden in the ITV comedy series Cold Feet. In 2017, she appeared as Emma Carr in the ITV drama series Endeavour.
